node.text:
@justineldridge Stops by and Chats with @thenineclub about his new golf company @thenumberthirtythree, dealing with injuries in the last few years, how one session got him on Chocolate, not knowing he was going to have a part in Yeah Right, dislocating his finger, filming clips in China, reviewing some of his skate clips and much more! Now playing at thenineclub.com 🎙
🎥: @tyevans @the_breadcrumb_trail
#JustinEldridge
#ChocolateSkateboards
